This is a brand page for the SAHUARO RECORDS trademark by Wilson; Floyd G. 
                                in Phoenix, , 85068.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this SAHUARO RECORDS trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Wilson; Floyd G. of the SAHUARO RECORDS trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the SAHUARO RECORDS trademark.
                           






On Monday, January 24, 1983,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        SAHUARO RECORDS by 
                        Wilson; Floyd G., Phoenix 85068.
                        The USPTO has given the SAHUARO RECORDS 
                        trademark serial  number of  73410675.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is CONTINUED USE NOT FILED WITHIN GRACE PERIOD, UN-REVIVABLE.
                        The correspondent listed for SAHUARO RECORDS is 
                        
                        
                                            C. ROBERT VON HELLENS of 
                                            CAHILL, SUTTON & THOMAS,  155 PARK ONE, 2141 E. HIGHLAND AVENUE PHOENIX, AZ  85016
                                .
                            The SAHUARO RECORDS trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Products & Electrical & Scientific Products
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for SAHUARO RECORDS 
                            is Phonograph Records and Prerecorded Audio Tapes. 
                            





