Insider Activity


Individual




Floyd C. Wilson



Mr. Floyd C. Wilson is Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at Halcón Resources Corp. and Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer at HK Energy Partners LP. He is on the Board of Directors at GeoResources, Inc. Mr. Wilson was previously employed as Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Petrohawk Management Co. LLC, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Petrohawk Energy Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Petrohawk Energy LLC, Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by 3Tec Energy Corp., President by W/E Energy Co. LLC, and Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer by Hugoton Energy Corp.



