Floyd C. Wilson
FLOYD C. WILSON is Chairman and Chief Executive Officer of 3TEC
Energy Corporation. He joined 3TEC Energy on August 27, 1999,
concurrent with the investment by W/E LLC. Mr. Wilson founded W/E
LLC in 1998. Mr. Wilson began his career in the energy business
in Houston in 1970 as a completion engineer. He moved to Wichita
